name: Spation
description:
Seventh stop of my Interstellar Journey; I now fully transitioned into this awakened state, leaving my past self behind, and at the moment I'm walking a new road. This time, it is not physical, but mainly mental, you could say even philosophical. Having stepped on to the other side, I'm now reborn, and can only have the futile hope that time forgets what I once was.
